                    or circumstances.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Founded with the vision of making mental health care more accessible, 
                    affordable, and stigma-free, MindEase connects individuals with licensed 
                    therapists and provides AI-powered tools for daily mental wellness management.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our team consists of mental health professionals, AI researchers, and 
                    passionate individuals who have experienced the transformative power of 
                    proper mental health care. Together, we're building a future where mental 
                    health support is just a click away.
                </p>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Services", "Home")" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Our Services</a>
            </div>
            
